title: Kerli - Love is Dead (2008) [FLAC]
description:
Please seed after you finish downloading, also I have a very slow connection so it might take awhile for me to finish seeding.

Of course if you like what you hear do buy the CD, it is even out on Island Records so even you Merkins can't complain that you would have to import from some small obscure German online shop.

And now for something completely different, if you like Kerli might I also suggest you listen to some Anne Clark, Emilie Autumn and Cristina (Monet).
